00:45:37,401 --> 00:45:38,861
All right.

567
00:46:01,925 --> 00:46:03,469
Yeong-bok.

568
00:46:10,267 --> 00:46:12,644
I just wanted…

569
00:46:14,313 --> 00:46:15,355
I…

