Of course. It's a feat.

601
00:49:36,056 --> 00:49:37,057
That's right.

602
00:49:37,974 --> 00:49:39,976
Okay, everyone.

603
00:49:40,060 --> 00:49:44,564
For Ms. Han Jeong-suk, who'll step forward
as a branch manager,

604
00:49:44,648 --> 00:49:47,442
